node.text:
👇 Spilling the secrets to how I built a 6-figure additional stream of income + 800K followers.

You might be surprised, but I did this ALL while:

✨ Not having anything to sell
✨ Not showing my face
✨ Not having a website
✨ Not being a whiz at tech
✨ Running my insurance + financial services business

And if I’m honest, I didn’t know what I was doing. I learned as I went.

In the past 2 years, I invested thousands of dollars in myself. Courses, mentors, ebooks—girlllll, you name it. 

I did it all and now I’m sharing with you EVERYTHING I learned. 

Literally holding NOTHING back, because I want you to succeed. And what better way than to tell you the exact 10 step process that took me from 0 ➡️ 822K.

💥 It’s your turn to CLAIM your success. 

Will you join the other 3,725 badass women on the waitlist for early access to The Ultimate Instagram Blueprint at HALF the launch price, 2 must-have bonuses, AND jumpstart your growth today?

Photo by Paula | Mindset & IG Expert on September 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Shannan Monson @shannanmonson when your boss asks you to meet unrealistic deadlines: "Happy to re-prioritize to make this happen. know it's important for the team. What projects would you like me to push back so we can make this happen in time?'.

Photo by Paula | Mindset & IG Expert on September 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Shannan Monson @shannanmonson when you've already said no and they won't take no for an answer: 'I've made my position clear, and it puts me in an uncomfortable situation when you ask again. I value our relationship and am asking you to respect my decision."'.

Photo by Paula | Mindset & IG Expert on September 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Shannan Monson @shannanmonson when the answer might be yes but the timeline is a no: "Thank you so much for thinking of me. I'd love to [do XXX] in the future, but can't make it work right now. Can we touch base again on [XX date]?'.

Photo by Paula | Mindset & IG Expert on September 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Shaan Monson @shannanmonson when you're afraid they will argue with your explanation for saying no: "Thank you for asking, but the answer is no and I'm firm in that decision." (no explanation necessary)'.

Photo by Paula | Mindset & IG Expert on September 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Shannan Monson @shannanmonson wher you want to say "no" right now but not "no" never love that idea, thank you for thinking of me! I'd love to [do XX] in the future but don't have the capacity to take it on right now. Please keep me in mind for next time!"'.

Photo by Paula | Mindset & IG Expert on September 14, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Shannan Monson @shannanmonson when someone asks you to work on something for free: "So excited for you and (the project they're asking you to work on). just worked on something similar for a client and the results were amazing! If you're interested in one of my packages, I'd be happy to set up a call so we can discuss the best fit. If you're looking for free resources, have an amazing (podcast/blog/free resource) that can help you get started here."'.

Photo by Paula | Mindset & IG Expert on September 14, 2021. node.text:
⛔️ Don’t let the idea of not knowing WTF you’re doing stand in the way of you building the life you love. 

Girl, let’s chat. 

It might seem like everyone’s got their sh*t together all the time, but it’s not the truth. 

🙄 the reality is that people are winging it as they go!

Ever heard of, “Fake it till you make it”? 

I want to let you in on a little secret… 🤫

I built up the @womanceomindset community without knowing what I was doing. 

All I knew was that I wanted to empower women around the world to build a life they love. 

🤣 The first ebook I ever sold? I did it myself from writing the pages to designing it on Canva. Oh, and I had no website, no email list, and no ads. 

Stop listening to what other people say you HAVE to do to run a business. 

Instead, just start. Figure it out as you go and do what feels right. 

And if you need extra support, get on the waitlist for my 10 step blueprint finally launching next week. I  give you the strategies I used to personally grow my own community to over 800k followers in just 2 years & business ❤️

We’re in this together!!

@womanceomindset 👈🏼Link in bio! 

Dream, Believe, Achieve 

Paula 🦋

I know that entrepreneurship is not easy. That’s why I built this community to empower you to chase your dreams & build the life that you love ✨

Paula💓
